</li>
<li class="rss-item"><a class="rss-item" href="http://feeds.nbcnews.com/c/35002/f/663286/s/30513372/sc/22/l/0L0Snbcnews0N0Cbusiness0Caugust0Ecar0Esales0Etrack0Ebe0Ebest0E20A0A60E6C10A984420A/story01.htm"  title="There may be all sorts of worrying signs about the economy b..." target="_blank">August car sales on track to be best since 2006</a> <br />
There may be all sorts of worrying signs about the economy but you could not tell that by visiting U.S. car showrooms. Sales of new vehicles in August are heating up, thanks to strong demand for trucks and crossover vehicles ? and the ample availability of financing for even riskier buyers.<img width='1' height='1' src='http://feeds.nbcnews.com/c/35002/f/663286/s/30513372/sc/22/mf.gif' border='0'/><br clear='all'/><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/sc/22/rc/1/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/sc/22/rc/1/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/sc/22/rc/2/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/sc/22/rc/2/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/sc/22/rc/3/rc.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/sc/22/rc/3/rc.img" border="0"/></a><br/><br/><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/a2.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/a2.img" border="0"/></a><img width="1" height="1" src="http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/174726126945/u/53/f/663286/c/35002/s/30513372/a2t.img" border="0"/>
